<text id="02-output-contract" title="Security Architecture Output Contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema (draft-07) for the spec artefact this methodology produces. Validator in scripts/validate-security-architecture.py enforces required keys, enum bounds, and pattern constraints.</summary>
  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/security-architecture.json",
  "type": "object",
  "title": "Security spec",
  "required": [
    "spec_id",
    "identity",
    "authz",
    "secrets",
    "threat_model_ref",
    "ci_controls",
    "incident_response",
    "version",
    "last_reviewed"
  ],
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "properties": {
    "spec_id": {
      "type": "string",
      "pattern": "^sec-[a-z0-9-]+$"
    },
    "identity": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": [
        "provider",
        "mfa_scope"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "provider": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 2
        },
        "mfa_scope": {
          "enum": [
            "admin_only",
            "all_users",
            "all_external"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    "authz": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": [
        "model",
        "tenant_filter"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "model": {
          "enum": [
            "rbac",
            "abac",
            "hybrid"
          ]
        },
        "tenant_filter": {
          "enum": [
            "rls",
            "query_predicate",
            "service_layer"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    "secrets": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": [
        "provider",
        "rotation_days",
        "per_service_scope"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "provider": {
          "enum": [
            "vault",
            "aws_secrets_manager",
            "gcp_secret_manager",
            "azure_key_vault"
          ]
        },
        "rotation_days": {
          "type": "integer",
          "minimum": 1,
          "maximum": 365
        },
        "per_service_scope": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "const": true
        }
      }
    },
    "threat_model_ref": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 5
    },
    "ci_controls": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 4,
      "items": {
        "enum": [
          "sast",
          "sca",
          "secret_scan",
          "iac_scan",
          "dast",
          "license_scan"
        ]
      }
    },
    "incident_response": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": [
        "paging",
        "tabletop_cadence_days"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "paging": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 3
        },
        "tabletop_cadence_days": {
          "type": "integer",
          "minimum": 30,
          "maximum": 365
        }
      }
    },
    "version": {
      "type": "string",
      "pattern": "^\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+$"
    },
    "last_reviewed": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "date"
    }
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>
  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "spec_id": "sec-storefront-2026-05",
  "identity": {
    "provider": "auth0",
    "mfa_scope": "admin_only"
  },
  "authz": {
    "model": "rbac",
    "tenant_filter": "rls"
  },
  "secrets": {
    "provider": "vault",
    "rotation_days": 90,
    "per_service_scope": true
  },
  "threat_model_ref": "docs/security/threat-model-storefront-2026.md",
  "ci_controls": [
    "sast",
    "sca",
    "secret_scan",
    "iac_scan"
  ],
  "incident_response": {
    "paging": "pagerduty:secops-rotation",
    "tabletop_cadence_days": 90
  },
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "last_reviewed": "2026-05-23"
}
]]></code>
    <note>All required keys present; enums and patterns satisfied.</note>
  </example>
  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "spec_id": "sec 1",
  "identity": {
    "provider": "",
    "mfa_scope": "none"
  },
  "authz": {
    "model": "trust",
    "tenant_filter": "vibes"
  },
  "secrets": {
    "provider": "env",
    "rotation_days": 0,
    "per_service_scope": false
  },
  "ci_controls": [
    "lint"
  ],
  "incident_response": {
    "paging": "",
    "tabletop_cadence_days": 1000
  },
  "version": "1.0",
  "last_reviewed": "today"
}
]]></code>
    <note>Forbidden traits: spec_id pattern violation; identity provider empty; enum violations in mfa_scope / authz.model / tenant_filter / secrets.provider; rotation_days out of bounds; per_service_scope false; threat_model_ref empty; ci_controls &lt; 4 or invalid; paging empty; version + date malformed.</note>
  </example>
  <reference path="scripts/validate-security-architecture.py">Validator script (stdlib-only, --help + --self-test).</reference>
</text>
